	    <td  bgcolor="dedede"  valign="top" class="msg" width="100%" >
         
          &gt;&nbsp;But I guess those were 24/7 figures, right?&nbsp; <br>  <br> Yes. <br>  <br> &gt; So I think it's probably a little silly to remove the battery every time you plug it into the wall. <br>  <br> I'd agree.&nbsp; Laptops are supposed to be convenient.&nbsp; But if you're using one in a long-term, fixed configuration on a desk, the battery is essentially in storage, and you might as well pull it out.&nbsp; Long term, hot, fully-charged storage, as when its plugged in, is bad.&nbsp; Either partially discharging the battery, or keeping it cool, helps a lot.&nbsp;  <br>  <br> It wouldn't be unusable for the battery compartment in an operating laptop to hit 40 C (or more). <br>  <br> The numbers I found for battery life remaining, per year,&nbsp;look like this: <br>  <br> <font face="courier new">Temp (C) 40% charge 100% charge&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Nickel (NiMH, NiCad) <br> 0&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 98%&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 94%&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; 99% <br> 25&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 96%&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 80%&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;97% <br> 40&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 85%&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 65%&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;95% <br> 60&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 75%&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 60% (3 months)&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;70%</font> <br>  <br> You can see it's both temperature and charge that hurt, and also that even high temperature doesn't hurt too badly unless the battery is near full charge. <br>  <br> <a href="http://www.batteryuniversity.com" target="_blank">More than you wanted to know about batteries</a> <br>  <br>  <br>  <br> <br><span class='ultrasmall'><b>Thumbnail Image</b></span><br><a href="http://ghguild.com/forum/upfiles.aspx/863/D56ED56B45C2491F99E2424439C8EBFF.gif" target="_blank"><img src="http://ghguild.com/forum/thumb.aspx/125_863/D56ED56B45C2491F99E2424439C8EBFF.gif"></a> 
          <br><br><img src='image/paperclip.gif' border='0' align='absmiddle'><a href="#" onclick="return uplwin('attachment.aspx?m=183925')">Attachment (1)</a>
		  <span class="info">
          					
			</span>
		 
         
         <div align="right">
         <br><span class="ultrasmall">(in reply to <a href='#183661'>nedd</a>)</span>
         
         </div>	
         
		</td>
